  "body": "<img alt=\"3a-IMG_1018.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/177a6d02fe7e19af.jpg?v=1782527896\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3b-unnamed-4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/836875daa97db567.jpg?v=1782527899\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-IMG_1070.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/47c2e341422436b3.jpg?v=1782527902\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3d-IMG_1075.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/085892e27b174541.jpg?v=1782527904\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3e-IMG_1061.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/aa537b80c4f1e3ab.jpg?v=1782527907\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-IMG_1080.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bbec9d7a2b0b4f74.jpg?v=1782527910\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-unnamed-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7307801ae400d62d.jpg?v=1782527913\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-unnamed.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0264805f830d6c1b.jpg?v=1782527916\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3i-IMG_1073.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/712e8dcfe2acbdd5.jpg?v=1782527919\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3j-IMG_0986.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/dd2e5dbc42b9675d.jpg?v=1782527921\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3k-IMG_1064.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c45ff93a3b0847e7.jpg?v=1782527924\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3l-IMG_1085.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6f383a04aa67ab5a.jpg?v=1782527927\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3m-IMG_1081.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cfeb5e32d83ebba0.jpg?v=1782527930\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3n-unnamed-3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3342607b716a772a.jpg?v=1782527933\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3o-unnamed-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1210633cb900e44a.jpg?v=1782527935\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>So many awesome moments from Creativation. As much fun as it is seeing brand new products, it's the connecting with people that tops it all off. Perhaps that's why I couldn't make <a href=\"https://youtu.be/i48L7xmVauU\">the video</a> any shorter, but I hope you enjoy it and feel like you were right there with us!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>On A Whim is now in stores - please check with your local retailer or shop online at <a href=\"http://bit.ly/onawhim\">Simon Says Stamp </a>and <a href=\"http://bit.ly/onawhim1\">Scrapbook.com</a>!  PS - We will be announcing our Design Team on Friday! Thanks so much for your patience!</p>"
